title: EP.57: PACKERS LOSE AGAIN, STEELERS UPSET, POTENTIAL TRADES, UPCOMING MATCHUPS, AND MUCH MORE!
description: Griffin is in shambles after Green Bay loses two straight games and he questions if they have what it takes to beat the commanders. Joe is riding high on the steelers upset win. We discuss other week 6 action as well as upcoming week 7 matchups. We talk about the world cup and which teams are looking good. Tennessee beating Alabama and storming the field was a sight to see. Tune in to find out more!
dc:creator: Griffin Proctor & Joe Jokonya
